  "2306490": {
    "name": "GNAW",
    "steam_appid": 2306490,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306490/extras/b1eedf3dee3d1cfcaec6da4b61f85f83.poster.avif?t=1770611331\" width=776 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306490/extras/b1eedf3dee3d1cfcaec6da4b61f85f83.webm?t=1770611331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>来认识一下麦克·雷普利！他胳膊虽短，却胸怀大志，梦想着能成就一番……大业。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新恐龙城是恐龙文明的心脏，一座熙熙攘攘的大都市，住满了大大小小的恐龙。所有物种都在此和平共处……或者说，曾经是这样，直到后来某种东西开始扰乱自然秩序。现在，麦克·雷普利深陷诡异科学和离奇事件的漩涡中，他必须揭开谜团，拯救世界于危难之中。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306490/extras/202ae481e48a4871028ddee5d7c3f60f.poster.avif?t=1770611331\" width=776 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306490/extras/202ae481e48a4871028ddee5d7c3f60f.webm?t=1770611331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>再非等闲恐龙</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >麦克·雷普利也曾是个安分过日子的普通恐龙，希望能出人头地。在经历一次离奇的科学事故后，麦克脱胎换骨了。如果你从未见过拥有异界之力的恐龙，那就准备好大开眼界吧——看麦克如何啃咬、吐射、吞噬他的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>奇异技能：咬出自己的风格</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每获得一项新技能，你都能解锁新方式，定制专属玩法。无论你是喜欢和那些恶心怪物贴身肉搏，还是拉开距离、远程周旋，抑或是远近结合，你都能打造出独一无二的麦克。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306490/extras/1c0e899f754db35e5285dc19d8cf9746.poster.avif?t=1770611331\" width=776 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306490/extras/1c0e899f754db35e5285dc19d8cf9746.webm?t=1770611331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>新恐龙城：享受璀璨霓虹，探秘危险暗巷</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新恐龙城里的故事和城里的恐龙一样多。在揭开匪夷谜团的过程中，你会遇到古怪的队友、扭曲的恶棍和变异的生物。所有这些离奇事件之间究竟有何关联？这就要靠你去发现了，不过动作要快，否则这座大都市恐怕就要彻底熄火了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>不是跑酷，是“恐龙跑酷”：畅游新恐龙城</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高楼林立、暗巷纵横，还有那看起来有点……不对劲的水。新恐龙城里应有尽有！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿梭于高楼密布、暗巷交错、奇景遍布的互连世界，深入调查城中的诡异事件。但务必要小心，危险就蛰伏在各个角落，等着你上钩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306490/extras/af5cd2af6f1e059aedaf4bf17bbe6545.poster.avif?t=1770611331\" width=776 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306490/extras/af5cd2af6f1e059aedaf4bf17bbe6545.webm?t=1770611331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>新恐龙城的下水道里有短吻鳄，是传说还是事实？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >究竟是什么导致新恐龙城里温顺的生物开始恐吓居民？你需要运用麦克的所有技能，搭配出巧妙的组合技，突破自我极限，才能战胜强大的敌人和恐怖的首领。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款跨越了2亿年时空的史前类银河恶魔城游戏</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >16种战斗与穿行技能，供你驱使</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获得新技能、开启新区域，在数十个区域之间穿梭、探索</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迎战150多种咆哮猛兽……然后把它们痛扁一顿</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结识新恐龙城中有趣的居民。还有格斯，而他嘛……你见了就知道了。</p></li></ul>",
